    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h3>Main Syntax</h3>

<ul>
<li><strong>without any prefix:</strong> normal local variables</li>
<li><strong><code>@</code>:</strong> instance variables</li>
<li><strong><code>@@</code>:</strong> class variables</li>
<li><strong><code>$</code>:</strong> global variables</li>
</ul>


